{
    "name": "Seance Medium",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Before Combat </b>The bard drinks a <i>potion of eagle\u2019s splendor</i>.<br/><b>During Combat </b>The bard disrupts spellcasters with <i>dispel magic </i>or readied blowgun attacks, and casts <i>blink </i>to protect himself in melee.<br/><b>Base Statistics </b>Without <i>eagle\u2019s splendor</i>, the bard\u2019s statistics are <b>Bard Spells Known </b>reduce spell DCs by 2; <b>Cha </b>20; <b>Skills </b>Bluff +21, Diplomacy +18, Disguise +7, Perform (act) +14, Perform (keyboard) +18, Perform (oratory) +14."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "Mediums prey on those who have lost loved ones, or sentimental souls who wish to contact the great beyond."
        }
    ],
